items.title: What we know so far about Washington DC plane crash
items.description: The aircraft collided with a military helicopter that was on a training flight as it approached the runway.

items.title: South Africa and Rwanda go head-to-head over DR Congo war
items.description: Rwanda says South Africa is in “no position to take on the role of a peacemaker or mediator” in DR Congo.

items.title: US and Russian figure skaters were on board crashed plane
items.description: They include two teenagers, their mothers and two former Russian stars, according to their club in Boston.

items.title: Merkel criticises her party leader after far-right vote
items.description: The former chancellor's comments come after the CDU put forward a proposal which was supported by the far-right AfD.

items.title: Man who burned Quran 'shot dead in Sweden'
items.description: Salwan Momika, 38, is reported to have been killed in an apartment in Södertälje, Stockholm.
